{
  "folder": "ruLW9Sc8sdXHlzEM",
  "name": "Wood Release: Foo Dog Heads",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "fhmozfgR9BgWG65F",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/items/foodogheads.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">You clap your hands together as you inject Chakra into the ground before conjuring 4 Wooden pillars that fill up to 4 different spaces that you can see with a Quake Shard that's 10 feet tall, 5 feet thick, made of wood, has an AC equal to your Ninjutsu save DC, and 25 hit points.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Each Earthen Construct emits a suppressive aura affecting creatures of your choice within 15 feet of each pillar. Select creatures who are within a 15-foot radius of a pillar at the beginning of their turns or would enter the radius for the first time on their turns, must make a Constitution saving throw taking 6d6 Chakra damage gaining 1 rank of Sealed on a failed save or half as much and no further effects on a success. A creature can only be affected by 1 pillars aura per turn.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the hit points of the Pillar by 15 and the damage by 2d6.</span></p>",
